{"tid":2192788,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔怕話畀你聽，我本來都係睇壹傳媒！」","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T11:47:50.000Z","uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95e61748693dd49572c348e94b86b28bb75228fc","tid":2192788,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"同學們都是「黃絲」，每次回校都會聽到他們不斷讚美壹傳媒，「成日話黎智英好好，蘋果日報守護真相」，而記協又有「洗腦教育」，所以我自然成為了一名「黃絲」。<br />\n<br />\n直至壹傳媒偽造訪問，我眼見「原來記協可以唔理發生乜嘢事」，「而家壹傳媒仲要話我無理指控？明明我只係公正地去投訴緊。」「啲記者喺度自己亂作故仔，我返工好辛苦，反而屈我自己講返工日日如是好悶！」其後我開始看《大公報》，了解到壹傳媒的陰暗面，「唔係啲所謂黃絲咁講話壹傳媒好好，又完全冇隱瞞市民咁」。"},{"pid":"dd931241bd7d0ccbf6b1cbd8e33b73566c8da66a","tid":2192788,"uid":276497,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"依啲文個格式已經睇到悶，「本來我都係&hellip;&hellip;架。」<br />\n2020咁撚多分化方法，仲出埋啲垃圾文死撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fe19afd59cd88868fae40a517cb4179f430364","tid":2192788,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"邊有人讚肥佬黎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老作都跟貼d啦"},{"pid":"f8e5a1fb1674c81c089e2983b3a1a5208a37def7","tid":2192788,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59fe19afd59cd88868fae40a517cb4179f430364","tid":2192788,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"邊有人讚肥佬黎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老作都跟貼d啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"侵：黎智英是個勇敢的人 向他問好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2165494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2165494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7756f308fa4018444af0a30b1ccecdbd93e5157","tid":2192788,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20